public static void show(AnalyzeCommand command,

                 throws GtpResponseFormatError
Parse analyze command response and display it on the board.

Parameters:
showTextBuffer - If not null, text lines from AnalyzeType.GFX commands will not be shown immediately in the status bar, but appended to the text buffer. This is for allowing multiline text in gfx commands that will be shown in a separate window later.
Throws:
GtpResponseFormatError
